  <!-- ============= DISTRICTS ============= -->
  <section class="section-gray">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Where our Thermador wall oven techs run calls</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Thermador built-in ovens cluster in specific LA neighborhoods — high-end kitchens, architect-designed builds, full custom cabinetry. Here's where we're out most weeks.</p>
      <div class="districts-grid">
        <div class="district">
          <h3>Beverly Hills · 90210 / 90212</h3>
          <p>Estate kitchens with dual MED302JS double combi-steam ovens, POD302W Pro doubles, and the occasional 27″ legacy built-in. Our most frequent Thermador wall oven zip.</p>
