          <p class="case-outcome">$165 total — no parts needed. Homeowner had been quoted $1,400 by another company for a "main control board replacement." That wasn't the problem.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="case-card">
          <div class="case-meta">Pasadena · 91108 · MED301JS single combi-steam</div>
          <h3>"Steam function stopped working — convection still fine"</h3>
          <p>Steam generator scaled up after 6 years without descaling — owner didn't know the cycle existed. Ran a full manufacturer descale with Thermador descaling tablets, cleared the water-level sensor fault, tested steam generation through three cycles to confirm stable operation.</p>
          <p class="case-outcome">$245 all-in including the descaling kit. Showed the homeowner how to run the cycle every 3–6 months going forward. Oven working like new.</p>
